==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Overweight
<hw>O"ver*weight`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Weight over and above what is required by law or custom.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Superabundance of weight; preponderance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overweight</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Overweight
<hw>O"ver*weight"</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Overweighing;
excessive.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Of no <xex>overweight</xex>
worth.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Fuller.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Having a weight in excess of what is normal, proper,
or expected; <as>as, the doctor recommends dieting to all his
<ex>overweight</ex> patients; <ex>overweight</ex> luggage will incur an
extra charge</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Overwell</ent>⟦br⟧
